    "caption": "Flew to Calorado on Friday, rented a Tesla, cranked the heat and slept in it for the night, it was -13 degrees Celsius outside of the vehicle.\n\nWoke up already in the mountains -- no drive, no hotel.\n\nSpent the day riding, then parked next to a random hotel lot and slept again in the same car.\n\nShower? Planet fitness is around the corner.\n\nNext morning I explored Denver a bit, took in the city, and on Sunday returned the car at the airport and flew home.\n\nNo days off.\nNo hotel.\n\n#adventure #mountains #snowboarding",
